message: If you use this work, please cite it using the metadata below.
type: dataset
title: Performance Evaluation of MoonGen and L2 Forwarder Latency Measurements on
  NIDA and CESIS Nodes
abstract: This dataset comprises measurements of network latency performed using the
  MoonGen load generation tool and an L2 forwarder component, libmoon. The experiment
  involved establishing a Digital Front-End Test (DUT) environment across nodes nida
  and cesis through automated scripts that cloned software libraries and configured
  virtual file systems. Multiple configurations of packet rates and sizes were utilized
  to assess system performance under simulated workload conditions. Evaluation outputs
  include CSV logs of latency data and associated image plots, generated by the load
  generation script, providing insights into resource utilization and potential bottlenecks
  within the libmoon forwarding process.
